{"tid":2495952,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"海賊王 ONE PIECE 1011話情報  下周合刊","createTime":"2021-04-19T13:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:32:25.000Z","uid":366271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"961a90f3bc64b655202c6349dd6f78a5f8324207","tid":2495952,"uid":366271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"[暫時得標題情報]<br />\n<br />\n第1次更新，超簡易情報翻譯 by【TalkOP漢化】韓文組  1圖，蒐集：TalkOP情報員 出處：TalkOP海道-海賊王論壇<br />\n1011話標題：紅豆餡的仁義（或紅豆湯/紅豆沙/甜豆沙/甜豆餡的仁義）<br />\n本話是大媽那邊的內容。<br />\n下期尾田不休刊（但本期JUMP為合刊，因此下周和下下週兩周只有1話海賊王看）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQadnmSf35h8PTRcy9pCzBGqpjNSWTHs3G6o2HG174YwK?filename=j43fDKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj43fDKU.jpg&h=c11219fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"823f9130104802d3cceb8fbcc1a56c33c26d5e86","tid":2495952,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11afb5f34592bd5131ec2c137ce921c01e069ca","tid":2495952,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"大媽叛變"},{"pid":"f37607c38e3754aad76f09f9b7c60ebadb1a3eeb","tid":2495952,"uid":335335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:33:15.000Z","msg":"大媽係咪終於要報恩<br />\n話哂錦衛門老婆同小玉係佢失憶果陣照顧過佢 仲請佢飲紅豆湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78373f4e2659597d3f2aa938a768e50df22f1046","tid":2495952,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1fb64611781fc47bb7366aa4d3450bafddf0c3b7","tid":2495952,"uid":394932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11afb5f34592bd5131ec2c137ce921c01e069ca","tid":2495952,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"大媽叛變"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"唔好啦"},{"pid":"6665a994e7d7a6a5fbee21a2b99660bd0e55e629","tid":2495952,"uid":394932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"盲猜係大媽撞到娜美烏索普小玉<br />\n然後大媽想殺娜美佢地 但見到小玉 就諗起紅豆湯之恩<br />\n所以無殺走左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d822fdde87be37c234e550317407065bae1bc745","tid":2495952,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"大媽食咗小玉嘅團子<br />\n<br />\n醒翻起細個同修女嘅約定<br />\n<br />\n「我會成為海賊王，然後你再來打敗我。」<br />\n<br />\n覺醒上翻去殺死凱多 打飛路飛<br />\n<br />\n然後消滅八成海賊"},{"pid":"d5fbc4f5e36e4f53b0a962228d5a43cf85226b1c","tid":2495952,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"大媽呢個角色根本就寫爛咗, 期待1011會有幾差。"},{"pid":"70151628d547cb9a61bb5b776803e49cb12054e9","tid":2495952,"uid":376713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"同我篇小玉情報文竟然差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}